      "role": "user",
      "content": "<|channel>thought\n<channel|>That's a good start for the general vibe. I want to get a bit deeper into the character dynamics for the script though. If I wanted to add some tension to the scene, what kind of conflicts or specific behaviors would be most \"realistic\" or common to see in that setting? Like, what are some of the more typical struggles or personality traits that usually come up in these kinds of family gatherings?",
